S.FORM: Brahim Ghali Pulasin Kali( Arapiya a sowal: Kuwaping a sowal: ) I 1949 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 16 a romi'ad masofoc ci Brahim Ghali, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Salawi Arapiya Finawlan Kapolong Kitakit ( Arapiya a sowal: ; Sipanya a sowal; República Árabe Saharaui Democrática SADR; Kuwaping a sowal: ) o kallopitahidang 0 West sahara; ) anini i ci Brahim Ghali, patirengan a romi'ad i 2016 a miheca saka 7 folad saka 9 a romi'ad. kasofocan a loma' lalamod salikaka natayalan pitooran
